metadata.name: Pablito
metadata.description:
Pablito was done in charcoal pencil, India ink, and oil pastel. His background is a made through tinkering with the Kaleidoscope feature in Pixlr. 

As my first mint, I invite you to look at Pablito and tell me who and what you see.

When I look at him, I see you a young man full of potential not yet realized. The background blooms signifying growth and he is crowned marking him as special in some way.
